Antennule (Fig. 
4a
) 0.65 times as long as cephalothorax; articles 1-4 with length ratio 1.00:0.37:0.33:0.03. Article 1 with two outer distal and one inner distal simple setae, and several proximal and distal PSS. Article 2 with three outer distal and two inner distal simple setae, and several distal PSS. Article 3 with two distal simple setae and several distal PSS. Article 4 with tuft of distal simple setae, distal PSS, and two aesthetascs.

